The paper discusses security and access control mechanisms for IoT systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the need for scalability and efficiency, which suggests that it may also belong to the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The focus on IoT devices and networks suggests that it may also belong to the categories of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and software engineering (cs.SE).
